'''Repabliki ya Cameroon''' goba '''Cameroon''' ke [[naga]] [[lefasana|lefasaneng]] la [[Afrika]]. Cameroon e bogarebodikela bja Afrika, e wela seleteng sa [[Bogare bja Afrika]].

Cameroon e agišane le :
* [[Nigeria]] (bodikela),
* [[Chad]] (leboabohlabela),
* [[Central African Republic]] (bohlabela),
* [[Equatorial Guinea]] (borwa),
* [[Gabon]] (borwa),
* [[Republic ya Congo]] (borwa).

